{"tid":659851,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"(有圖)第一次食到流心嘅豬柳蛋","createTime":"2018-05-10T08:05:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-12T02:27:30.000Z","uid":104658,"like":70,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"53558713e5bce9acc6e5c090054349c9a2747507","tid":659851,"uid":104658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T08:05:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/10/155958_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F10%2F155958_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=bf793612&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n平時叫親豬柳蛋隻蛋都煎到老哂  一d都唔好食<br />\n<br />\n咬落去第一啖有d蛋黃漿流出黎  慢慢滲入個包皮到<br />\n<br />\n人生第一次食到  好感動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65dc601015d95f8f872f34c1ba1fa0a00336a35a","tid":659851,"uid":28515,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T08:09:09.000Z","msg":"攝影大師"},{"pid":"bde7f7ac07b9f5438d50bf3478f4b868a3dc083c","tid":659851,"uid":52571,"like":8,"dislike":30,"score":-22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T08:14:15.000Z","msg":"師兄啲牙都幾唔齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5c20526aabc998b2a8a35fd129f6553def0a1a6","tid":659851,"uid":10788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T08:14:19.000Z","msg":"n年前食過 超撚正"},{"pid":"a200f0b562757d9b70a0598954843f2bc9421651","tid":659851,"uid":10788,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T08:15:40.000Z","msg":"我上次食果個再生d 流心d 可能條友煎到悶 唔跟時間指示 整流心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3bc0e0a95061ff6c01195a480cb9d588ac277bd","tid":659851,"uid":104658,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T08:16:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/10/161446_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abdde